The Federal Reserve Board has nonews conference or announcement planned for today, a Fedspokesman said, dispelling market rumors that a statement waspending.    "No such event is scheduled or planned," said spokesman BobMoore.    Rumors of a pending Fed announcement or news conferencecirculated in financial markets, following a government reportthat consumer prices advanced by 0.4 pct in March, suggesting arapid rise of inflation. Reuter&#3;